msgid "Even with these tools there is danger of data corruption/loss, so only do this if you are willing to live with that risk. In particular, be aware that **Google Drive** is incompatible with calibre, if you put your calibre library in Google Drive, **you will suffer data loss**. See `this thread <http://www.mobileread.com/forums/showthread.php?t=205581>`_ for details."
